{"tid":1518428,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【太古站槍擊義士】傳真社：生產商列明 Tippmann 胡椒球彈近距離發射嚴重可致命","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:56:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6085fba76aa63fa178435daf51cad51cb84ff1a9","tid":1518428,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1477777_1_L_20190830163209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1477777_1_L_20190830163209.jpg&h=8bae57e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月11日有警員在太古港鐵站其中一個出口，以胡椒球槍近距離射向示威者。警方曾於記者會表示，發射距離約一至兩米，並確認當時達到安全的距離。傳真社翻查生產商使用指引，發現安全警告列明應避免向距離少於1.8米的人士發射。另外多款警方用過的子彈型號，生產商指引都列明擊中頭部有致命風險。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社說，多次在示威現場觀察，根據速龍小隊使用的胡椒球槍槍身字樣，找到生產商的使用指引，說明該槍子彈射程超過45米，應避免向約1.8米內的人士射擊，意外射中眼部有機會造成永久傷害甚至致命。根據生產商指引，子彈能非常準確地擊中目標，如射向頭部、頸、胸、心臟或脊骨可引致嚴重受傷或死亡。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社並引述英國廣播公司記者說，曾被警方子彈擊中面罩，令面罩損毀，根據現場所用催淚彈和橡膠子彈的彈殼型號，生產商列明不可直接向人射擊或者近距離發射，否則會引致重傷或死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Tippmann-Custom-Platinum-Paintball-Gun/dp/B07BZZNJ99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTippmann-Custom-Platinum-Paintball-Gun%2Fdp%2FB07BZZNJ99&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=c4e34d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Tippmann-Custom-Platinum-Paintball-Gun/dp/B07BZZNJ99</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61edXNTFu3S._SX425_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61edXNTFu3S._SX425_.jpg&h=796bf221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64bceda9c175788c1225eab799245ec7b2804a38","tid":1518428,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"傳真社<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/